==Regional variations==
The leader of the Wales Green Party is Anthony Slaughter, who was elected as the party&#x27;s leader in December 2018. Some regional and local groups have adopted a gender balance principle and emulated the Principal Speaker structure, including the LSE Students&#x27; Union Green Party, who have a Female and Male Co-Chair.

