===Organized crime===
A number of high-profile organized crime figures hail from Bensonhurst, including Frankie Yale, Anthony Casso, Paul Castellano, Mikey DiLeonardo, Anthony Gaggi, Dominick Montiglio, Carlo Gambino, John Gambino, Sammy &quot;The Bull&quot; Gravano, Gregory Scarpa, and Carmine Sessa.

